<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 15:13:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>越南国家主席会见美国大使呼吁加强防务和经济关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vietnam-president-meeting-with-us-ambassador-calls-stronger-defence-economic-2024-06-13/</link><description>政府表示，越南新当选的总统苏林周四呼吁加强与美国的关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 15:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/vietnam-president-meeting-with-us-ambassador-calls-stronger-defence-economic-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷总统米莱将在中国会见习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/argentina-president-milei-meet-with-xi-china-2024-06-13/</link><description>据当地报纸《Clarin》周四报道，阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱将在未来几周内访问中国并会见中国国家主席习近平。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/argentina-president-milei-meet-with-xi-china-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示，美国就业市场类似于大流行前的环境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-market-resembling-pre-pandemic-environment-yellen-says-2024-06-13/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦 (Janet Yellen) 周四表示，美国就业形势越来越类似于 COVID-19 大流行之前存在的就业市场，工资增长放缓并不构成通胀的威胁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-market-resembling-pre-pandemic-environment-yellen-says-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>印度拉贾斯坦邦发现部分 MDH 和珠穆朗玛峰香料食用不安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-rajasthan-finds-some-mdh-everest-spices-unsafe-consumption-2024-06-13/</link><description>一封信显示，印度拉贾斯坦邦告诉联邦政府，随着当地和全球对这些品牌涉嫌污染的审查力度加大，经过测试发现一些流行品牌 MDH 和 Everest 的香料“不安全”食用。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-rajasthan-finds-some-mdh-everest-spices-unsafe-consumption-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国奇瑞汽车：欧盟工厂将有助于降低电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-auto-eu-factory-will-help-mitigate-ev-tariffs-2024-06-13/</link><description>中国出口量最大的汽车制造商奇瑞汽车 (CHERY.UL) 一位高管周四表示，预计其在欧洲的生产计划将有助于抵消欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车进口关税的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-auto-eu-factory-will-help-mitigate-ev-tariffs-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>英国首次针对违反俄罗斯石油限制的船只实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-imposes-first-sanctions-targeting-ships-breaching-russian-oil-restrictions-2024-06-13/</link><description>英国周四对俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京“影子舰队”的船只实施了首次制裁，称这些船只是用来规避西方对俄罗斯石油贸易的制裁的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 12:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-imposes-first-sanctions-targeting-ships-breaching-russian-oil-restrictions-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫表示与朝鲜建立更密切关系的权利不容置疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-its-right-closer-ties-with-north-korea-should-not-be-doubt-2024-06-13/</link><description>克里姆林宫周四表示，俄罗斯与朝鲜发展更密切关系的权利不应受到任何质疑或恐惧，并表示两国关系的潜力非常深厚。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 11:42:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-its-right-closer-ties-with-north-korea-should-not-be-doubt-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国吉利对欧盟关税决定表示失望，誓言采取“必要措施”维护权利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-expresses-disappointment-eu-tariff-decision-vows-necessary-measures-2024-06-13/</link><description>中国汽车制造商吉利汽车周四对欧盟提高中国制造电动汽车关税的决定表示“非常失望”，并誓言“采取一切必要措施”维护其合法权利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 11:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-expresses-disappointment-eu-tariff-decision-vows-necessary-measures-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>加税后特斯拉预计将提高中国产汽车在欧盟的售价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-expects-hike-price-china-made-cars-eu-due-tariffs-2024-06-13/</link><description>特斯拉周四在其网站上表示，由于欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车（EV）征收进口关税，该公司预计将提高其 Model 3 的价格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:27:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-expects-hike-price-china-made-cars-eu-due-tariffs-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：外交官称，中国在瑞士峰会前推动乌克兰和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-pushes-rival-ukraine-peace-plan-before-swiss-summit-diplomats-say-2024-06-13/</link><description>十名外交官表示，中国没有参加周末的乌克兰和平计划峰会，而是一直在游说各国政府制定替代计划，其中一名外交官称北京的行动是对瑞士全球会议的“微妙抵制”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-pushes-rival-ukraine-peace-plan-before-swiss-summit-diplomats-say-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储加息后的第二天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-13/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 展望未来一天的市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:04:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业保留要求欧盟调查猪肉、乳制品的权利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-reserve-right-request-investigations-into-eu-pork-dairy-2024-06-13/</link><description>当被问及行业组织是否正在游说其这样做时，中国商务部周四表示，中国企业保留对欧洲乳制品和猪肉进口提出反补贴和反倾销调查的权利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:21:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-reserve-right-request-investigations-into-eu-pork-dairy-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国关税反应的不确定性，欧洲汽车股下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-auto-stocks-fall-further-concerns-over-chinas-tariff-response-2024-06-13/</link><description>欧洲一些最大汽车制造商的股价周四进一步下跌，原因是中国可能如何应对欧盟对中国进口电动汽车征收的新关税，以打击布鲁塞尔认为来自北京的过度补贴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-auto-stocks-fall-further-concerns-over-chinas-tariff-response-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>微软总裁将就安全漏洞向众议院小组作证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-president-testify-before-house-panel-over-security-lapses-2024-06-13/</link><description>微软总裁布拉德·史密斯将于周四在众议院国土安全小组作证，回答有关该公司在过去一年中俄罗斯和中国黑客入侵其系统后的安全实践的问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-president-testify-before-house-panel-over-security-lapses-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>BRC 首席执行官表示，Shein 在加入英国零售集团时致力于可持续发展和劳工问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-committed-engage-sustainability-labour-when-joined-uk-retail-group-brc-ceo-2024-06-13/</link><description>该行业机构负责人告诉路透社，快时尚集团 Shein 在被允许加入英国零售联盟 (BRC) 后，承诺参与可持续发展和道德劳工政策等问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 08:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-committed-engage-sustainability-labour-when-joined-uk-retail-group-brc-ceo-2024-06-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>